        <Summary xml:lang="en">Cross-platform 3D game interpreter which allows you to play LucasArts&apos; Lua-based 3D adventures</Summary>
        <Description xml:lang="en">ResidualVM is a game engine reimplementation that allows you to play 3D adventure games such as Grim Fandango and Myst III.
